name: quiet trails
description: The trail meanders ahead, curving around until the path becomes hidden to the eye.

name: ornate railings on the stairs
description: The railings are lined with gold and helped the king walk to his chambers.

name: x
description: This crows' nest is very small and has some bird poop around and lots of emeralds inside

name: very long table with ornately carved legs
description: The long table had carved legs that were very much over decorated.

name: chairs whose legs match the table legs
description: The chair has intricately carved legs that look to be four ladies holding the chair up.  The wood gleams warmly as it has been carefully polished with beeswax.

name: ornate throne
description: With its torn seat and dusty surface, it is clear that no body sat upon it for some time.

name: clothes line
description: The rope stretched a few feet and was at eye height. Strung tight between two metal poles.

name: pew
description: this pew belonged to an old church. It's made out of light wood and it's very sturdy

name: mosses
description: Curly and soft, like a thick blanket, the moss looks like it could be a good place to rest.

name: campfire burning
description: The campfire has a bright red glow to it, it's flames reaching to shoulder blade height.

name: ship
description: The ship is worn and decrepit from long battles at sea.

name: gold cups
description: The ornate gold cup is wide at it's stop and has a narrow base, it's gold plating embroidered with King's crest.

name: silver spoons
description: The spoon is very tarnished and in need of polishing

name: treasure chests filled to the brim with gold
description: The treasure chest has intricate details and can be locked.

name: nests
description: The nest appears to be abandon.

name: burrows
description: It was unclear what animal carved it out, but the burrow extends far beneath the land past the sunlight's reach.

name: dens
description: The den was so big and made of rocks, some people were afraid to explore it.

name: inkwell
description: The inkwell lay tipped over, it's well stained with dried ink.

name: writing desk
description: The writing desk is scattered in papers, and as you move closer, you can see the surface is worn from years of use.

name: parchment
description: The parchment is crisp with age around the edges and covered in a thin layer of dust.

name: jugs
description: The jug is sealed up tight, containing liquids of an unknown origin.

name: bar
description: The bar is empty with few customers inside, and a bit shabby in appearance.

name: drinking glasses
description: The glass is chipped on one side, but appears to you to be sturdy and well-made.

name: steins
description: The ceramic stein has once seen better days, or far too many merry days, and is now beginning to crack on it's white painted surface.

name: welcome mat
description: A old welcome mat that has seen many travelers. The word welcome can barely be seen through all of the fading.

name: rack
description: the rack holds many different things upon it

name: mattress
description: The mattress is stained with blood.

name: chifferobe
description: The chifferobe is heavily lacquered and gleaming in the sunlight. You thought to yourself that if the chifferobe is this fancy, the items inside must be unbelieveable.

name: troll's bed made of rotting hides
description: The troll's bed looks disease-ridden to you. The hides that make up the bed are matted and dirty.

name: vials,
description: The vial is partly filled with a liquid substance. You wonder what manner of strange concoctions it's contained throughout the years.

name: small pot
description: This small clay pot has beautiful flowers drawn on one side. it's old but not cracked

name: large shelf
description: The shelf is wooden and large. You can see that it is meant to support many heavy objects and is functional and not decorative in nature.

name: roaring fireplace
description: The fireplace contains large logs inside its stone frame. The roaring fire licks the chimney as it expells heat.

name: metal bucket
description: The bucket is rusted and old.

name: metal meal tray
description: The tray is made of metal and is cool to the touch.  There are sections to put food on the tray.

name: king's throne
description: Gold and precious jewels adorn the king's imposing throne. The seat contains one large plush red velvet cushion.

name: altar
description: The alter is littered with offerings, and bares an inscription in a strange, mysterious language.

name: pews
description: The pew is made of wood and is very long.

name: fire pit
description: The fire pit is powerful and hot. It burns with a special intensity.

name: large green land
description: The large green land is covered in dew, with a few muddy patches where mist has mixed with soil.

name: gates
description: for many the gates of Hades look like the gates to a garden in which to forget all of their troubles.

name: baptismal font
description: The baptismal font sits full of water still and clear.

name: broken windows
description: The window is old and coated in dust, the wood on its sill has just about rotted away.

name: furniture
description: this piece of furniture is one of a kind.

name: execution stand
description: the execution stand post is ready to execute the prisoners who have started the rebellion against the King

name: signs
description: The old wooden sign, tattered and tilted to one side, presents a stark warning to travelers -- "Beware."

name: few rusted pieces of block
description: The block seems to have had a letter engraved on it, though now you can barley make out what it is under all the rust.

name: stand
description: The stand is a bit rickety and worn out from use.

name: old machinery
description: The machinery has many elaborate parts and spindles.

name: rock walls
description: The rock wall has very little upon it, its cold surface mostly impenetrable, but a lone torch holder is fixated on it in order to provide some light.

name: marbled floor
description: The floor is made of an elegant marble, with shades of white and gray visible.

name: floor decoration
description: This floor decoration is very unique. Looks like a very expensive type of wood, very rare

name: flags
description: The flag flaps in the wind. The streaming ends a tattered reminder.

name: velvet seats
description: The velvet seats are smooth and brand new.

name: stage
description: The stage is well taken care of, and it's wooden floor is smooth and clean. It's canvas top shades it from sunlight on hot summer days.

name: garden bench
description: Then bench is long enough for everyone to sit on.

name: swing
description: The swing shows some rot in the rope and seat, but still works.

name: rug
description: The rug is ornate and detailed. You think the owner must have paid a hefty pricce for something so exquisite.

name: closet
description: The closet is dark and contains handmade blankets and a cloak.

name: wooden chair
description: The chair was tattered and worn after many years of use in the old theater.

name: small wooden bowl
description: You could tell the bowl was crafted entirely by hand without tools. Its lip was uneven, and its wall varied in thickness. But despite its misshapen appearance, it kept a man's porridge warm.

name: lantern
description: The wooden lantern has a glass cage that served to hold a candle inside and preserve it from the elements. It has a circular bronze handle at the top to be easily carried.

name: bedding
description: The bedding is soft and warm, and is made out of silk and stuffed with animal feathers.

name: ships

name: cargo crates
description: A protective box used for the storage and transport of cargo.

name: fishing nets
description: In its tangled mess, you see a shining object.

name: cases for jewels
description: The outside of the case has a design of flowers painted on it. On the inside, its lined with velvet.

name: empty coin bag
description: The coin bag is devoid of anything of value. You knew this before even looking, but still held a small amount of hope that your fortunes has changed.

name: floor
description: The floor is made of marble with detailed carvings of past wars.

name: carpets made of silk
description: The carpet is smooth and colorful. Since it is made out of silk, it is very light weight.

name: cup
description: The cup is old and broken, with the handle chipped from being dropped

name: seats
description: This seat looks to be made of some type of wood, and has been polished by many a rear resting upon it.

name: pole
description: the pole is old and run down. there are still brackets that used to hold relevant signs years ago.

name: piano
description: The piano has weathered keys turned yellowish from decay.

name: racks
description: The rack appears to be made out of iron, and it is rusty in a few places.

name: huge ovens
description: This yellow huge oven has many cooking options.

name: trash bin
description: The trash bin overflows with rotten vegetables and flies.

name: serving platters
description: The serving platter is clearly very old, but it has been polished recently and it gleams in the light.  Someone has taken very good care of this platter over the years.

name: ornate desk
description: This ornate desk is beautifully decorated. There are some names engraved on it, possibly the names of the kings

name: bookshelves
description: The bookshelves reach to the ceiling, full of worn, leather volumes of bound tomes.

name: winding stairs
description: The stair is winding in design and seems to go on up forever.

name: observation deck
description: A platform used to observe the scenery around the location.

name: beautiful farmland
description: This farmland is the largest in the village and it requires many peasants to work it.

name: walls
description: The wall is easy to climb since it is entirely made of jagged stones stacked like stairsteps.

name: stove
description: The stove radiates heat, the wood burning red hot within can only be described as inviting.

name: trays
description: A heavy wooden tray is covered in scratches and stains from long use. It has handles on the side for carrying.

name: hitching post
description: The hitching post is worn and splintered from use.

name: old broken tiles
description: Upon closer inspection, the tile seems coated with a mixture of candle wax and lamp oil. Whoever did this hope to cause someone pain.

name: deck
description: The deck is made of wood and weather beaten.

name: barrel of salted herring
description: The heavy wooden barrel reeks of it's content, the salted herring giving off an odor most foul.

name: firewood
description: The firewood has been chopped nicely.

name: stool
description: The stool is sitting alone asking for someone to sit on it

name: tomb
description: The tomb is falling apart, and the remains inside have been disturbed.

name: utensils

name: place mats
description: The place mats are stained, old and mismatched.

name: bowl of fruit

name: sandy beach
description: The sandy beach is occupied by the king's royal guard to defend against intruders.

name: wooden platform

name: lush maroon carpet

name: barracks
description: The rickety wooden barracks display their aging wooden boards eaten through by termites.

name: anvil
description: The anvil is hevay and black and appears to to have been well-used.

name: uniforms
description: The uniform belongs to someone of great importance to the kingdom.

name: small wooden table
description: The table is made of the highest quality wood.

name: small pool of water
description: the water is clean and safe for drinking.

name: jug of water

name: serving dishes

name: small table
description: The table is just large enough for four people to sit at it. The wood appears old and worn.

name: wooden cranes
description: The wooden crane is cracked and rusty from lifting the king's heavy furniture

name: unfinished navy ships
description: The ship is covered in barnacles as if it had been long at sea.

name: targets
description: The target is littered with holes from past arrows that had hit their mark.

name: bench made of stone
description: The bench seems heavy and impossible to move.

name: bucket for eliminating waste
description: The bucket is filled with a noxious brown liquid.

name: gold-laced furniture
description: The furniture is ornate and gold laced.  It is fit for a king.

name: bed
description: The bed is small and narrow. It looks like it might be for a child.

name: bear- and tiger-skin rugs
description: The rug was soft and roughly cut. You wonder what happened to the animal it came from.

name: basket
description: Such a worn out basket. It can barely hold all the fresh-caught fish. It has mold on it and it's broken in many parts

name: piece of old, sun-bleached sailcloth
description: It could be a very old piece this piece of cloth, maybe it was worn by someone important or has a story

name: fish tank
description: The empty fish tank is covered in dust and broken at the bottom, unable to hold water.

name: small bucket
description: The bucket may be small but it gets the job done.

name: more-than-king-sized bed
description: looking twice at the bed, surprisingly it is more than a king sized bed

name: chair
description: The chair is inviting, but it is not the time to sit for a rest.

name: chamber pot
description: The chamber pot smells terrible, like it has only been hastily emptied and not cleaned.

name: large ornate table
description: The table has a highly polished surface, ornately lathe-turned legs and intricate floral carvings along the edge of the tabletop.

name: smaller tables
description: The table is low and small.  It looks like it could be used as a dinner table for a small child.

name: higher dining table
description: The table stood as well as it could, as one leg was noticeably well worn out.

name: golden goblet
description: The goblet is made of fine gold and is very well made.

name: stained glass windows
description: The glass window is old and dusty with small pieces of glass falling out

name: musty shelf
description: The shelf is worn and its nails are coming loose from the wall.

name: table
description: The table is large and made of wood.

name: bridge
description: The bridge has a few missing boards and looks like it might not be safe to cross.

name: benches

name: fountain

name: wooden bowls

name: chimney
description: The chimney is dirty and messy

name: dinner table
description: The table is small and square. It is sturdy and has different shades of brown.

name: silks
description: The silk has many colors and is very soft to the touch.

name: huge bed
description: This bed could easily fit a family of four on it, it is quite massive.

name: brook
description: This brook burbles cheerfully, and looks crystal clear and very refreshing.

name: small wooden bed
description: this small wooden bed is clothed in warm cotton blankets. it has a homely feel, and seems to be slept in by a small child

name: colorful homemade quilt
description: The quilt's colors are bright and vibrant, singing a song of praise to its creator.

name: small wooden cabinet
description: The cabinet has two wide doors on the front concealing a shelf inside. It is made entirely of oak wood.

name: straw mattress
description: The mattress is worn down, and may have bed bugs.

name: comfortable chair
description: This chair is crafted of wood, and looks to be carved to perfectly accommodate anyone who might sit in it.  It seems the sort of chair you could spend many an hour in.

name: bed
description: The bed is made and seemed be untouched since morning.

name: beakers and potions
description: The beaker bubbles and the potion undergoes a strange reaction.

name: huge vat of brewing liquid
description: The huge vat of brewing liquid is boiling over.

name: small fountain

name: walls
description: The wall appears to be heavily damaged. There are chips and holes throughout.

name: torture rack
description: The dried blood upon the rack is mortifying.

name: crooked stone chimney
description: It is thick with soot. You may find something hidden if you look into the dark interior.

name: large four poster bed
description: Such a sturdy large four poster bed. The metal frame is a bit rusty but still looks fancy

name: finest linens
description: The linen is very soft to the touch and has a carefully embroidered pattern.

name: large chest of drawers

name: wooden spit
description: The wooden spit shows signs of repeated use.

name: colorful lizard
description: There are so many hues of green on the lizard, it can't easily blend in with many trees and plants.The lizard's neon yellow skin is so bright that it is impossible for it to camouflage itself in the wild.

name: cups
description: The cup is brown and made of hardened clay.

name: wooden cups

name: stretched canvas
description: The canvas lay bare, waiting for the painter to begin his work.

name: baby bassinets
description: A bassinet is woven from strands of fine linen.

name: boxes
description: It's a cubical box with a crest on the side.  It looks perfect for storing all kinds of items.

name: cabinet
description: The cabinet contains dishes and cups and is very dusty.

name: silk pillows
description: A dark red liquid has stained the king's large, purple silk pillow.  It appeared to be either blood or red wine.

name: wooden cart
description: The wooden cart has a platform made from sturdy worn boards. Its large wheels keep it from getting stuck in the mud.

name: hard wooden chair under the eaves
description: This hard wooden chair under the eaves is made out of pine, it has wine stains on it, also it's all scratched up

name: docks
description: The dock is large and sturdy against the coming tides.

name: buckets
description: The wooden bucket is beginning to warp and you don't know whether it will hold water or not.

name: broken pottery
description: The broken pottery's artwork is unrecognizable. What was once a piece of art is now just shards of colorful figures.

name: basin
description: The basin is stained from use and one of the handles seems to be broken.

name: nice fruit trees
description: the fruit tree bears many fruits at this time

name: incense holders
description: The incense holder is covered in ashes.

name: wood aisles
description: The aisle is between the rows of seats. It is wide enough for three men to walk abreast.

name: big wooden table
description: The table is large, with rough boards and a few knot holes in the wood.

name: scale
description: The alchemist's scale was made of solid gold.

name: porcelain vase

name: basket of grain

name: small lake
description: The lake is a bit murky in terms of its waters but seems to be mostly calm.

name: bathroom pot
description: The notorious pot holds a stale liquid.

name: well
description: The well is worn out. Those who once used it are gone.

name: stall
description: It is tall and rather dusty, like nobody has sat on it for a while.

name: pail
description: The pail is old and beginning to rust in places.

name: broken lanterns
description: The lantern's glass that once protected the candle is broken and the wood itself is splintered and worn.

name: beach
description: The meeting of sandy shores with dancing blue water. This beach has been around for ages.

name: large and well stocked wine rack
description: The rack is being used to store an extensive collection.

name: luxuriously soft couch
description: The couch has a velvet soft covering that shimmers under the light.

name: green short grass
description: The short grass feets good under your feet and the green reminds you of spring.

name: small alter
description: The alter has darkened with age and small amounts of splinters can occasionally be seen.

name: empty gruel bowl
description: Grit and grime cake the edges of the heavily used bowl.

description: The oak pew looks like it has been here for many decades.  Someone has carved their initials in the seat.

name: large table

name: simple wooden table
description: The table is light in color and made from a common wood. It seems relatively new.

name: single shelf
description: The shelf is sturdy and made of wood.  A few items sit on the dusty shelf.

name: rough stone floor
description: The floor is well worn with uneven stones.

name: furniture
description: The furniture is wooden and handcrafted.  It is sturdy.

name: water wells
description: The well is deep and dark; a cool breeze rises up from its depths.  Looking down, you can see the gray slime that has formed on its close-fitting stone sides.

name: loft
description: It's a cozy looking, well kept loft.

name: big organ

name: altar
description: The altar, made of fine marble, is humbled by blood stains.

name: forge
description: The forge is dark and steamy with a musky scent.  It is mysterious and enchanting, repelling the observer while pulling them in.

name: wooden workbench
description: This workbench looks quite worn from years of use, and has odd divots in the wood where a project might have gone astray.

name: shrine
description: The shrine is meticulously clean, and it holds a few offerings and some incense.

name: expensive carpet
description: A carpet made of the finest silk and with intricate patterns woven in.

name: wooden chest
description: the wooden chest contains the special items of the man's past.

name: guard's toilet basin
description: You see a rancid toilet basin. Its stench fills the air.

name: fire pit
description: The fire pit is rather large and can be used.

name: fountain
description: The fountain flows red with the blood of soldiers.  The stone is stained red, and no water emerges from the spout.

name: jar of seeds
description: The jar contained an assortment of seeds, varying in size and color. But unlike the seeds, which had long expired, the dusty jar is certain to be given a second life in the future.

name: money box
description: The money box is made of hard steel and looks like it could withstand an attack from any weapon imaginable.  A rusted padlock secured the lid.  It looks like it hasn't been opened in ages.

name: land
description: Vast green reaches as far as the eye can see, the land is well preserved and manicured.

name: grimy stools
description: This stool is old and dusty and has a broken leg

name: wooden bar

name: wooden tables
description: The table is old and broken with scratches on the surface.

name: candy shop

name: roads
description: The road is dusty, desolate and eerie.  It has a sense of danger around every corner.

name: streets
description: The street is made of cobblestone, one of the first of its kind.

name: cobblestones
description: The cobblestone is hard and cool to the touch. It has traces of dirt and grass all over.

name: well
description: The well in the center of town is the best source of information around.

name: cargo
description: The cargo is stacked up neatly.

name: wooden cabinets
description: The cabinet is made out of oak. It is filled with plates and glasses.

name: basin for water
description: The pottery basin is chipped on one side.  Upon closer inspection, you see that it is also cracked.

name: steering wheel
description: It is obvious this steering wheel had been used many times.

name: wooden floor
description: A flat surface for walking, made of oddly shaped boards, which were strategically fit together.

name: wine glasses
description: the wine glass has a lovely shape.

name: coffins
description: The coffin is clearly very old and covered in a layers of dust.

name: wood flooring
description: An expanse of wooden boards that have been cut to fit together.

name: big bed
description: The bed creaks easily, its wooden headboard worn smooth by years of use.

name: sitting bench
description: Upon closer inspection one can see the bench is in need of repair.  Weather has taken its toll.

name: fountain
description: Though it still looks like it could, the fountain is no longer working.

name: wooden bed

name: desk

name: fire pits

name: altar
description: The altar is made of wood and looks well worn.

name: draw bridge

name: pots

name: plates
description: the plate is exceptionally colorful and interesting

name: elaborate carpet pieces

name: brick walls

name: pink and white outline

name: wooden stool
description: The stool is old and uneven.

name: kettle

name: small bed

name: desk
description: The desk is made of sturdy oak but is very low to the floor.

name: polished gold

name: barrels for crops

name: dirty trail

name: mattresses

name: double thick wooden door

name: ornate chairs
description: With hand-carved lion faces and coat of arms and a frame made of solid mahogany the ornate chair is fit for royalty.

name: water troughs
description: The wooden trough is broken from holding the heavy water and grass

name: small gazebo
description: This small place is perfect for merryiment and joy.

name: trash bins

name: beds
description: The bed is elevated off the ground, but still shows signs that something had chewed through it.

name: altars where they kneel in prayer

name: trapdoor

name: rivets

name: flasks

name: purses

name: sheets
description: The bedroom sheets are old and dirty after not being ished for months

name: well

description: on closer inspection the animal looks edible and it's bones can be used as small daggers.

name: stolen food
description: He sits with the food he stole, a feast to be had.

name: basket
description: The basket appears to be filled with a harvest of freshly picked apples.  There is a small scroll sticking out of the top of the bounty.

name: barrels
description: The barrel fills to the top and sparkles with clear liquid.
